{"tid":1863852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地專家解釋咩叫「糞口傳播」","createTime":"2020-02-05T10:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T10:33:17.000Z","uid":163529,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fde23b2c51212eb1c5ae59b7102d9571d2601bfb","tid":1863852,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:13:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZCDUz5U8v8k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZCDUz5U8v8k&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=f0c34c7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZCDUz5U8v8k</a><br />\n<br />\n原來平時上面食開屎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3151e57580355c267b7e3a0f7f6b32d0814d82a0","tid":1863852,"uid":163529,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:13:57.000Z","msg":"仲要建議大家勤洗手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食屎前要洗手？！"},{"pid":"0d369855890dd5233acda47100206e52d6291a63","tid":1863852,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:14:42.000Z","msg":"支那人食開屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2fc74ff7b953993d2cee2cdbf3a977186359b09","tid":1863852,"uid":258770,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"其實你聞到屁味就等於d屎入左你個鼻到"},{"pid":"d132a19b5a1bf73c3ab42d23f8e8ddfd13ff2ed6","tid":1863852,"uid":3454,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2fc74ff7b953993d2cee2cdbf3a977186359b09","tid":1863852,"uid":258770,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"其實你聞到屁味就等於d屎入左你個鼻到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"思覺老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n很多時候，大家在街上的行人路上都會見到新鮮狗屎。有些是完好的，沒有被人踩中，但有些是有個大鞋印的。被人踩中的狗屎的周圍，都會有狗屎印，有些印是很清楚可見，很容易避開，但有很多被人踩了很多次，這樣狗屎印便會越踩越難被人發現，而且也會令原來有狗屎的範圍越踩越大，結果就只會令更多人踩中狗屎，但現在講到的人，都只是一部份人，這篇文的題目，是【人人都在踩狗屎】，為現在只是一部份人？在以下的文字，我會解釋！既然一篤屎都可以令這麼人踩中，這樣如果一條街有兩篤狗屎，這樣便會有更多人踩中了！但這文的要點不是有多少篤的問題。有多少篤當然是一個踩中狗屎的因數，但大家有沒有發覺，當一篤屎被很多人踩過之後，這篤屎好像是消失了，這是很多人的一般想法，但事實並不是這樣，這篤屎只會越踩越大篤，只會令更多中招。世界上的所有物質都是由分子組成。一篤狗屎，是因數以兆億計的狗屎分子組成。一篤狗屎被很多人踩過之後，不論在任何天氣清況都會很快變乾，變乾了的狗屎粒子，會除風飄到到處都有，有些會散到地上給人任踩，有些會飄到人的鼻子裡。這個世界相信有數以千萬篤狗屎在街頭。所以人人一出街，都是踩著狗屎的，不單只踩，因為狗屎粒子是到處飄，所以人人都是食過狗屎的！"},{"pid":"79016a3f02d02f466bcbd12f72dcdc986b1a1dc9","tid":1863852,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2fc74ff7b953993d2cee2cdbf3a977186359b09","tid":1863852,"uid":258770,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"其實你聞到屁味就等於d屎入左你個鼻到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:22:47.000Z","msg":"耳鼻喉通"},{"pid":"c8bb26e96918c2820893dd380481441b6fe7dfcd","tid":1863852,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDPGeQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDPGeQ.png&h=f227900c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家疫情有爆發跡象，十萬火急！藍田女手足全家確診武漢肺炎，請大家幫手簽下面的聯署：<br />\n<br />\n另外大家亦可以透過聯署同twitter自行遊說美方人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呼籲研發出肺炎解藥的美國藥廠供貨香港救手足救香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcatywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=ad497784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-supply-remdesivir-drug-which-can-treat-2019-ncov-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n給予港府壓力封閉所有連接中國大陸的口岸<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/exert-pressure-hk-government-close-all-borders-mainland-china-prevent-outbreak-wuhan-pneumonia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fexert-pressure-hk-government